{"tid":843251,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺 FPS 出咗之後就入唔到錢去 IB？","createTime":"2018-10-01T04:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T04:26:09.000Z","uid":39122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e64e8b40a9773e64b9898ac6b597d199358a80a6","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"以前用開 CHATS / ECG 入 HKD 去 IB，<br />\n尋日用 FPS 試，轉完出去就即刻退錢入嚟，今朝再試都係咁。<br />\n打上銀行問，佢話 IB 個 account number 唔存在，所以啲錢彈咗返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關 Citibank N.A. 啲 virtual account number 事。<br />\n啱啱喺 IB 開咗 support ticket 問，等緊佢哋回覆。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打呢兩日成功入到錢？"},{"pid":"0f054e2b2f64e1b7f302d3aff366442cd20903ef","tid":843251,"uid":187956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"佢個account number好似每個客都unique<br />\n所以FPS用唔到掛 留名睇IB點覆"},{"pid":"5b0526810b653b739a32a7471ece03ce7e1d88ac","tid":843251,"uid":103996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，btw, 樓主 fail 果下有無畀人扣手續費？"},{"pid":"d2d83643c25728e052cebaa3d1744b4ac90fb04c","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b0526810b653b739a32a7471ece03ce7e1d88ac","tid":843251,"uid":103996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"我都係咁，btw, 樓主 fail 果下有無畀人扣手續費？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"暫時望落冇罰手續費。<br />\n<br />\nIB 初步回覆我話佢唔覺個自己 system 有問題，<br />\n不過叫我畀啲轉帳嘅 screenshot 佢睇吓駛唔駛再 escalate 上去。<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴打都入唔到錢去 IB，<br />\n不妨自己都去 IB Portal 開張 support ticket，<br />\ncap 返轉帳確認嗰版同埋佢彈返轉頭嗰條數（假設你入 $10,000 畀 IB，你會見到你個銀行戶口 <span style=\"color: red;\">-</span>$10,000 同埋 <span style=\"color: green;\">+</span>$10,000 兩條 record），<br />\n等 IB 留意到其實佢（或者應該話佢個 banker Citibank N.A.）個嘢壞咗。"},{"pid":"6370a38a01067e6d905653e314e85531ffef9ad5","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"搞掂咗，推返個 post 先。<br />\n<br />\nIB 確認咗係 Citibank 唔識報 IB 啲 VAN 畀 FPS，<br />\n所以其他銀行以為呢個 account 唔存在，<br />\n就取消啲客嘅轉帳指示。<br />\n<br />\n試咗由大貓射出到 IB send bulletin 話入咗數，<br />\n前後大約 45 分鐘左右。<br />\n同以前 CHATS 比唔係特別快，<br />\n但起碼唔駛趕喺下午 bank close 前打 CHATS 指示，<br />\n可以放工返到屋企先慢慢搞都得。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話時話，真係冇人發現呢幾日 IB 入唔到錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd85f851346131a7299845fae5a6d4c24d72c2f8","tid":843251,"uid":59648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6370a38a01067e6d905653e314e85531ffef9ad5","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"搞掂咗，推返個 post 先。<br />\n<br />\nIB 確認咗係 Citibank 唔識報 IB 啲 VAN 畀 FPS，<br />\n所以其他銀行以為呢個 account 唔存在，<br />\n就取消啲客嘅轉帳指示。<br />\n<br />\n試咗由大貓射出到 IB send bulletin 話入咗數，<br />\n前後大約 45 分鐘左右。<br />\n同以前 CHATS 比唔係特別快，<br />\n但起碼唔駛趕喺下午 bank close 前打 CHATS 指示，<br />\n可以放工返到屋企先慢慢搞都得。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話時話，真係冇人發現呢幾日 IB 入唔到錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"弊啦, 我今朝用hsbc fps過數<br />\n依家ib戶口仲未收到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbfa32b70aec037aacd4a465b29246e7b78a732","tid":843251,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93eaa0ec0f3b5b69d7236b1d4768dcd1d36274e6","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd85f851346131a7299845fae5a6d4c24d72c2f8","tid":843251,"uid":59648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6370a38a01067e6d905653e314e85531ffef9ad5","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:37:42.000Z","msg":"搞掂咗，推返個 post 先。<br />\n<br />\nIB 確認咗係 Citibank 唔識報 IB 啲 VAN 畀 FPS，<br />\n所以其他銀行以為呢個 account 唔存在，<br />\n就取消啲客嘅轉帳指示。<br />\n<br />\n試咗由大貓射出