<br />\n前後大約 45 分鐘左右。<br />\n同以前 CHATS 比唔係特別快，<br />\n但起碼唔駛趕喺下午 bank close 前打 CHATS 指示，<br />\n可以放工返到屋企先慢慢搞都得。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話時話，真係冇人發現呢幾日 IB 入唔到錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"弊啦, 我今朝用hsbc fps過數<br />\n依家ib戶口仲未收到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"睇吓 eBanking 有冇退錢，<br />\n冇退錢嘅話 cap 齊啲圖，<br />\n回想返今朝入錢個時間（大約），<br />\n去 IB Portal 嗰度開個 support ticket 追。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:32:11.000Z","msg":"個cs只係話唔見有錢, 同埋收到錢之後會通知我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就斷咗綫"},{"pid":"6ce48c466caf446e62e4c5b29be1e13c8ef206f6","tid":843251,"uid":119535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"可以用FPS過錢去IB? 我以為未開始商用<br />\n直接打ib畀嗰個account no就得？"},{"pid":"d9c491cce19fffa3aada39dbc6db1044eff52b72","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ce48c466caf446e62e4c5b29be1e13c8ef206f6","tid":843251,"uid":119535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"可以用FPS過錢去IB? 我以為未開始商用<br />\n直接打ib畀嗰個account no就得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"你冇得揀，因為 FPS 嘅出現同時係 ECG 同 CHATS 嘅謝幕。<br />\n係，都係照打 bank code、branch code 同 account number。"},{"pid":"41c4a9122a1ca4fdfa13e4f8daa53aebb41fecf2","tid":843251,"uid":57431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"你想用FPS入錢落IB, 首先係要知道ib 係 citi na真正既account number<br />\n不過如果FPS 轉數無reference既，你唯一既方法都只會係CHATS. VAN係citi na內部用，唔應該會上到FPS"},{"pid":"e61af409319c8f6a7a261b1733d2b9a835382b7f","tid":843251,"uid":124056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6370a38a01067e6d905653e314e85531ffef9ad5","tid":843251,"uid":39122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-